`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- The model follows an async Msg/Cmd pattern: each background fetch returns a typed `Msg` struct, matched in `coreUpdate`. The sprint fetch will follow exactly this pattern (`SprintIssueKeysMsg` → `handleSprintIssueKeys`).
